data.description: Three Bedroom One Bath Home located on a quiet street in Orchard Mesa. Modern updates include stainless appliances, anew gas stove, remodeled bathroom with tiled shower and hard surface flooring throughout. The living room features a bay window to add natural sunlight and a fireplace to cozy up to. The outdoor space and large fenced yard offers just as much, complete with covered deck for backyard BBQs, mature trees that provide plenty of shade, large drive way for the extra cars and RV Parking and two storage sheds. The automatic sprinkler system is hooked up to irrigation water which comes with the property for all your lawn and gardening needs. This home is perfect for the first-time homebuyer, someone looking to downsize or the investor looking to add to their portfolio.
